attributes.title: NEW YEARS FIREWORK DISPLAY • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this weeks Behind the Cow Chop, James and Trevor put together a spectacular firework celebration for everyone in the Cow Chop house.

attributes.title: PEPPER SPRAY DANGER • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this week's Behind the Cow Chop, we take you behind the Pepper Spray Gauntlet and show you more of the dangers of pepper spray.

attributes.title: BOO WARDROBE MALFUNCTION (+RT UPDATE!) • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Fireworks!! ... if they work. And everyone gets dressed up for another round of Mario Party. The gang is lookin' good until Aleks realizes his costume is missing a key component: the hood. Also, be sure to check out the important Rooster Teeth update from Brett!

attributes.title: 32 POUND MARSHMALLOW BATH • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this weeks Behind the Cow Chop we take you behind the scenes with 32 Pounds of Marshmallows and we setup for our 1000 degree knife video.

attributes.title: GETTING KICKED OUT • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this week's Behind the Cow Chop we have the unfortunate news that we are being kicked out of our house. There are a couple more videos from the house which will be uploaded this week. We are still in the process of figuring out a temporary situation before moving to LA, and plan to keep you all updated. Thank you for all your support guys!

attributes.title: ON THE STREETS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this week's Behind the Cow Chop we have a bunch of updates to give you all. Thanks for all your support guys.

attributes.title: CRICKET CANDY • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this week's Behind the Cow Chop, Trevor chews on some cricket candy, James spends most of his time trying to get a rug down from the ceiling, and Aleks is just checking the place out.

attributes.title: SLINGSHOT AMUSEMENT • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Unopened Walmart Delivery toys are put to the test. Getting messy with the paintball gun leads to looking through merch and changing into some fresh Cow Chop duds on the spot. And this is how we deal with the terrible bug infestation at the barn...

attributes.title: HOW TO CALCIFY YOUR HOUSE + RT Update • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Aleks misses his cue and a random stranger has to explain the Rooster Teeth fundraiser. Brett explains why we dropped below Platinum. Finally, we get to show you how that hole in the wall happened at the old Cow Chop house.

attributes.title: WACKY PRANKSTERS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Time to check out a Prank Kit that James got a long time ago. There are lots of pranks, but Aleks is having none of it

attributes.title: LET’S COSPLAY: BARN EDITION • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Let's cosplay: barn edition! Watch the guys' slow but sure transform into Link and Dark Link. Also, were you wondering why Trevor dressed up as Max Payne for his trip to Boston? Watch to find out!

attributes.title: GOOD-BYE BARN + RT Update • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Time to say good-bye to the barn, and hello LA!

attributes.title: GOING PLATINUM (ALMOST) • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Cow Chop! There was down time while bleaching the boys' hair, and things got interesting. Whose desk is whose? And there's an update on Trevor's hair.

attributes.title: HOT DOG COCKTAIL • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: This week on Behind the Cow Chop, we take a look at what exactly went into the meal James ate during the Gourmet Insect Dining Nightmare video, and watch James' Yelp review on that "restaurant". Also, join the guys on a walk through Texas as they venture out to get some Denny's.

attributes.title: FAST & FURIOUS TARGET PRACTICE • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: In anticipation for an upcoming video, Aleks tests out a BB gun to see how bad it actually hurts. Then, watch Aleks and James get dressed in their cosplay for the Fast and Furious game.

attributes.title: BUTCHERING A DILDO • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: The moby dildo stank up the men's bathroom after we moved in. It was a very weird smell. We received several complaints, so it was time for that bad boy to go. No regrets and strangely satisfactory.

attributes.title: SCIENCE OF THE DUNK • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: LIFE IS PAIN KIDS. NEVER FORGET IT     Can the boys dunk? Probably not. Asher and Trevor try a little science experiment, but don't really try at all and give up before even beginning.

attributes.title: WET MULTIPLAYER VR • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Scenes! This week we get dressed up for an NBA game, play in our own water park, and there's a little sneak peek into the multiplayer virtual reality set-up we created.

attributes.title: PARKING IN MARKIPLIER’S SPOT • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: This is the fear and anxiety you have to live with when you park in Markiplier’s spot. Also, we got a bunch of new stuff, so check it out!

attributes.title: GETTING ON THE GUEST LIST • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: In this weeks Behind the Cow Chop watch as the crew ventures to E3.

attributes.title: SURVIVING E3 AND CHINA TOWN • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to more Behind the Cow Chop! Join us on some more E3 bits and getting hassled in China Town.

attributes.title: BORDERLINE HEATSTROKE • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Cow Chop! First check out the sweet soccer-mom-rental-van we got. And it's all smiles when we leave, but on the way back, it's clear everyone almost had a heat stroke. After that, hop on a ride with Joe in China Town. Finally, take a look at the location where we shot the Golden Squiggly Cup Promo video (spoiler: it's not pretty).

attributes.title: THE MISSING TAPES • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: THE LOST FOOTAGE HAS BEEN FOUND! Welcome back to more Behind the Cow Chop! In January of 2017, a handful of YouTubers were evicted in the suburbs near Littleton, Colorado while shooting videos for their channel.           In their haste to escape, they left behind one box full of dildos and a single tape of ""behind the scenes"" footage.           Six months later, that footage was found.

attributes.title: WHEN LIFE HANDS YOU LEMONS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: This week on Behind the Cow Chop, we check out Steven Suptic's sweet pad, extra adorable pups, and even his trash all while he's not home! Then, do you know what goes into making fake vomit for the big screen? Well we don't either, but it might look something like this. Finally, what're we going to do with these helium balloons left over from the pilot episode of I'll See It When I Believe It? When life hands you lemons...

attributes.title: DELETED SCENES • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this weeks Behind the Cow Chop we show you some deleted scenes from our new pilot episode of I'll See It When I Believe It. We also venture to RTX with some extra shenanigans.

attributes.title: HOT CHEETOS PIZZA IS FIRE • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Half the office stops everything they're doing to try Hot Cheetos pizza. Turns out the pizza is too hot for anyone to handle. And then it's time for a fire safety lesson.

attributes.title: WATER CLEAN UP FIASCO • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: After Aleks' spa day, there was a huge mess to clean up. Now everyone has to pitch in to keep the office from turning into a swamp. And Aleks has another box of presents for Trevor and himself.

attributes.title: INSANE MAGIC TRICK • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Are you ready for some magic and some music and maybe some fire? Get ready for this week's Behind the Cow Chop.

attributes.title: GERMANY TRIP & LOGO RIP-OFFS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: This week on Behind the Cow Chop, we take a look at Brett's exciting trip to Germany. Then, Trevor is given a Roblox toy that should bring him inspiration for a new career. Finally, Aleks has a new shirt for Joe, but it looks suspiciously familiar.

attributes.title: THE ACCOUNT OF ALEKS BLOOPERS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back! This week we have bloopers from The Account of Aleks video. Please go check it out if you haven't already! Also, a few of guys went to PAX West last weekend and met a lot of great people and signed a ton of merch; we wanted to show you a little bit from that.

attributes.title: NEW COUCH + TARGET PRACTICE • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: This week on Behind the Cow Chop, James shows us some new fun toys he got, Crossbows! Also we finally got our new couch!!!

attributes.title: MECHANICAL BULL TRIALS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Scenes! Did you ever wonder how much it costs to rent a full-on mechanical bull for a day? Watch to find out! And check out the rest of the crew try their hand at bull riding! Also, when James buys a new toy for the office, everyone gets really excited to play with it, even when it hasn't been used in the main video yet (oops!).

attributes.title: OFFICE PILLOW PROBLEMS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to more Behind the Cow Chop! This week we found a popcorn-scented-pillow on the ventilation pipe above our heads; this could be considered a possible hazard. The only way we know how to get it down though is to throw more pillows at it. Will that work?! Then, Trevor gets a present from someone. Watch to find out what it is!

attributes.title: WORLD WAR II BLOOPERS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back! This week we have  bloopers for the Raid World War II gameplay. Be sure to check them out if you haven't already. Also Trevor gets some new sweet glasses for everyone and shows Brett some tasty bubbles.

attributes.title: LEWD DISNEY KNOCKOFFS - Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to more Behind the Cow Chop! Things got musical this week. We opened some packages from some cool companies. And as per usual, something broke. Don't point lasers in your friends' eyes, guys.

attributes.title: COW CHOP HIRES A DEMON • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Here is some spooky Behind the Scenes!

attributes.title: KEYBOARD MEMORIAL VIGIL • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Cow Chop! This week Trevor caused some controversy with his big Shaquille O'Neil feet. Join us for our memorial service held in this episode of BTS.

attributes.title: LOBBY MAKEOVER • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Cow Chop! This week we're doing some warehouse reno, including painting over that big M in Brett's office and sprucing up the lobby. Just how tacky can we make it?

attributes.title: WRESTLING PRACTICE • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description:
This week on Behind the Cow Chop we take you inside one of the training sessions for our WWE 2K18 Tournament.
Also, James lays some eccentric flavors of chocolate on us, and we sit down for a heart to heart with Joe.

attributes.title: GETTING IN THE HOLIDAY SPIRIT • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: Welcome back to Behind the Cow Chop! Let's get into the holiday spirit! We're decorating our set this week, and James is under pressure to make sure all holidays are accounted for.

attributes.title: HOLIDAY(S) UNBOXING(S) • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: The Hanukkah decorations showed up this week, just in time to win Jakob back over; at least we hope. We also open one present under our tree early because it was sent in by a devoted fan. Just how devoted, you might ask? Permanently so... unless Aleks changes her mind.

attributes.title: STUN GUNS AND SECRET SANTA • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: The day had come to receive our Secret Santa gift courtesy of Rooster Teeth. All Farid had told us is that our gift would "either be a godsend or a pain in the ass." Not knowing what to expect, we decided to prepare for the worst by testing our new stun guns out on, who else but, ourselves. Good thing we did, because as soon as Sugar Pine 7 showed up we had our hands full with something a lot bigger than two high-voltage electroshock weapons.

attributes.title: IT'S BEGINNING TO LOOK A LOT LIKE COW CHOP CHRISTMAS    • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description:
Ho ho holy snappers! Wait until you see this Christmas tree that Aleks got for the Cow Chop warehouse.
We had a lot of help getting it in, that was the easy part; decorating it, however, was a TALL order.

attributes.title: Holiday Video • Behind The Cow Chop
attributes.description: This is the holiday Behind the Cow Chop video... enjoy!

attributes.title: BEACHES AND DRAGONS • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: Khail and Aleks take Trevor on a trip to the beach while Brett and Aleks give you a special sneak peek of our new DnD show, Class of 198X.

attributes.title: PARACHUTING OFF THE ROOF • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this week's episode, the guys discover a door to the roof where they test the laws of gravity. Aleks gets sent free Adidas merch and James gives Aleks the best toast he's ever had.

attributes.title: COCKROACH INFESTATION • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: An uninvited guest makes its way into the warehouse and James Willems gives the guys some new workouts to whip them into shape.   The following is for those multicultural. attributes.title: SPICY SAUCE AFTERMATH • Behind the Cow Chop
attributes.description: On this weeks episode we are gonna burn our tongues and insides with spicy food!
